{"tid":2377210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔鬥藍唔鬥黃．純支持廣東話奇案Channel (1)","createTime":"2021-01-23T11:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T11:59:53.000Z","uid":249675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2374379715bc86280da350a5f2e3f22ea905eb","tid":2377210,"uid":249675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">自從以前聽摩星嶺．一路都對D靈異奇案鬼鬼怪怪好有興趣<br />\n最近成日都WFH無所事事．發現有幾個呢類型又唔錯嘅廣東話Channel<br />\n終於唔撚洗再聽D普通話Channel<br />\n推薦比大家排名不分先後！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins><span class=\"blue\">原子檔案 Mr.Atom</span></ins></strong> (創於2020年3月25日)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1S5-u-C0JKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1S5-u-C0JKE&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TasWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=7ade9ab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1S5-u-C0JKE</a><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">穩定一星期一片．相對算係同觀眾互動比較多<br />\n最近嘅片加入左心理測驗元素．創意加分<br />\n缺點係除左youtube比較少其他平台見到佢嘅蹤影</span></span><br />\n---------------<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins><span class=\"blue\">Highway Recording</span></ins></strong> (創於2017年5月9日)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WBZ8ZnrKFzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWBZ8ZnrKFzU&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TasWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=8c2dbdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WBZ8ZnrKFzU</a><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">Channel比較悠久．題材比較多<br />\n影片大多靜止畫面．簡單較偏向電台節目形式<br />\n唯獨關閉留言區．同觀眾零接獨</span></span><br />\n---------------<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins><span class=\"blue\">解謎檔案</span></ins></strong> (創於2020年11月2日)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zw2tGBlbPyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fzw2tGBlbPyo&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TasWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=266fa5d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zw2tGBlbPyo</a><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">算係比較新晉嘅Channel．之前以黃色Youtuber係連登出過Post<br />\n影片數量比較少．比較難加以評論<br />\n但係比較新．應該有其他發展空間</span></span><br />\n---------------<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><ins><span class=\"blue\">解密工作室</span></ins></strong>  (創於2020年3月3日)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DF6rKfEThn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDF6rKfEThn8&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TasWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=f9f9fdec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DF6rKfEThn8</a><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">算係當中發展得最快．<br />\n係好多不同類型平台都見到佢出現．仲有同果籽合作<br />\n亦都有Phone In講鬼故環節．但係質素有待改善</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">如果大家有其他Channel推薦！歡迎分享！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e34bd5922466f76a86633035dbc279850fc5fff","tid":2377210,"uid":74567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"花家姐係咪藍？"},{"pid":"9d1200c5e8bda34eb99086a418bbe3def984a04d","tid":2377210,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"屌你藍字點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08b23c64a92abf0723c75fdec84433490ebf6f4","tid":2377210,"uid":249675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1200c5e8bda34eb99086a418bbe3def984a04d","tid":2377210,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"屌你藍字點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"sorry 係我錯  即改唔好屌"},{"pid":"19e7812fca58c8ce231fd686361a22f9af8264ea","tid":2377210,"uid":249675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1200c5e8bda34eb99086a418bbe3def984a04d","tid":2377210,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"屌你藍字點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg